<h2 id="api-routes">API Routes</h2>
<h3 id="auth">Auth</h3>
<ul>
<li>POST /register â€” Register a new user</li>
<li>POST /login â€” Login</li>
<li>POST /logout â€” Revoke current access token</li>
<li>GET /api/me â€” Get current authenticated user</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="tasks">Tasks</h3>
<ul>
<li>GET /api/tasks â€” List tasks</li>
<li>POST /api/tasks â€” Create task</li>
<li>GET /api/tasks/{task} â€” Get a single task by Task ID</li>
<li>PUT /api/tasks/{task} â€” Update task (full)</li>
<li>PATCH /api/tasks/{task} â€” Update task (partial)</li>
<li>DELETE /api/tasks/{task} â€” Delete task</li>
<li>PATCH /api/tasks-status/{id} â€” Update only a taskâ€™s status</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="todos">Todos</h3>
<ul>
<li>PATCH /api/todos/{id} â€” Update a todo status</li>
</ul>
